{"3389290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Naughty Store Manager", "steam_appid": 3389290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/68e4efde441c41994d5cac18032540a2.avif?t=1747041255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras_big/68e4efde441c41994d5cac18032540a2.avif?t=1747041255 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《頑皮商店經理》是一款模擬遊戲，你需要在父親去世後管理一家繼承的商店。除了商店，你還繼承了他欠一個黑幫成員的債務。唯一的出路是升級商店並還清貸款。幸運的是，你有很棒的員工來幫助你！這會帶來什麼？在《頑皮商店經理》中找到答案吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/4d6f2c46e6aefa3a615208f515b22da5.poster.avif?t=1747041255\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/4d6f2c46e6aefa3a615208f515b22da5.webm?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/4d6f2c46e6aefa3a615208f515b22da5.mp4?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/929e88e837745c3c01bc98ea7f52d272.avif?t=1747041255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras_big/929e88e837745c3c01bc98ea7f52d272.avif?t=1747041255 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/771c3b3d5854541e9cecc359aa4f8925.poster.avif?t=1747041255\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/771c3b3d5854541e9cecc359aa4f8925.webm?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/771c3b3d5854541e9cecc359aa4f8925.mp4?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琳是持有經理債務的黑幫成員的女兒。在她父親的要求下——這無法拒絕——她開始在商店工作。她來自一個特權背景，一切都被給予她，她成為了經理負責監督的對象</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/9657acb1acd83056f4a71d54c0cc9840.poster.avif?t=1747041255\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/9657acb1acd83056f4a71d54c0cc9840.webm?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/9657acb1acd83056f4a71d54c0cc9840.mp4?t=1747041255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直央是商店裡最有經驗的員工。她已婚，丈夫每天接送她上下班。雖然她曾經很外向，但婚後生活變得單調。儘管如此，她對他人仍保持著善良和積極的態度。由於與丈夫超過十年沒有親密關係，她在性方面仍未得到滿足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras/39e9b422f521d1ccb5941faf55909423.avif?t=1747041255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3389290/extras_big/39e9b422f521d1ccb5941faf55909423.avif?t=1747041255 width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14個性愛動畫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把貨架填滿，保持倉庫整潔，處理垃圾，不要跳過清潔——顧客們正在結帳處排隊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿上超市經理的鞋子，體驗一個充滿曲折的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >照顧你的團隊，保持他們的士氣高漲，建立關係，挖掘他們的內心！</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"